<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石猴冲过大瀑布，落进了一个大洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他瞪大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27942</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞里有很多竹子、树，还有美丽的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27943</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞壁上长满了青苔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一条小溪在洞里流着，闪着光，空气里有很多水雾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石猴发现了一张长桌，桌上放着碗、杯和碟子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墙边还有一个火炉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在洞的深处，石猴找到了许多屋子，里面有很舒适的床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瀑布外面，其他猴子都盯着瀑布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们觉得他成功了吗？”有只猴子问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。”另一只猴子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他可能被瀑布水流冲到下面的河里去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然—水花四溅！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石猴从瀑布里冲了出来，直接落在了猴子们面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还活着！”一只猴子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石猴大笑起来：“当然！我们太幸运了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我为大家找到了一个完美的家。跟我来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石猴又跳进了瀑布里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有的猴子挠挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这看上去还是太危险了。”有只猴子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们试一下吧。”长臂猿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿过了瀑布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后，另一只猴子也跳了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他的猴子也跟着跳了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快所有的猴子都来到了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都在洞里跳来跳去，看这看那。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个洞真美。”长臂猿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些猴子打了起来，相互叫嚷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们开始抢碟子和碗，还有些猴子抢卧室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我先看到这张床的！”一只猴子大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是！”另一只猴子不甘示弱，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我先看到的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石猴看了一会儿他的朋友们，然后交叉着双臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃哼！”他清了清嗓子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的猴子都停下来看着石猴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我为大家找到这个洞的。”石猴说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就意味着我现在是你们的王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们为什么不向我鞠躬呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大王说得对。”长臂猿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向石猴鞠躬，说：“参见美猴王！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他猴子也跟着鞠躬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“参见美猴王！”他们大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多年过去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们白天在树林和小溪里玩耍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上就在洞里睡觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天晚上，猴子们举办了一场盛大的宴会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水果和坚果堆满了桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232966</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们唱歌跳舞，还有音乐伴奏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王坐在他的宝座上微笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他的笑容很快就消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>长臂猿看到了之后，马上走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大王！”长臂猿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您看上去不太高兴。出什么事了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王叹了口气：“我们在这里的生活很美好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对啊，确实很美好。”长臂猿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那您为什么不高兴呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王半天没说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他说：“总有一天我们会离开这个世界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，我希望可以永远这样幸福地活下去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>长臂猿的眼睛一亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。”他说，“您想长生不老吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我想长生不老。”美猴王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>长臂猿摸了摸下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么您必须跟着圣人学习。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>圣人是非常有智慧的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们可以将自己变成其他动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们可以在天上飞来飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也知道怎样才能长生不老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王又笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我去哪里可以找到圣人呢？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您必须找到有人生活的地方。”长臂猿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在那儿您会找到圣人的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>349758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王就做了一个小木筏，并在木筏上装了食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>349759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>356632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把木筏推入了小溪，随后自己跳了上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>356633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>木筏开始顺水漂流，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>363266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王向他的朋友们挥手告别。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>363267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>366693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心！”他大声叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>366694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>370959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等我学会长生不老之术，就会回来的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>